    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a reliable but well-used option for a budget-conscious buyer. While it runs well and has been regularly serviced to ensure safety on the road, please expect some notable cosmetic wear. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dings, and the interior shows signs of age with some staining on the upholstery and wear on the steering wheel. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation without the premium price of a newer-looking car.",
      "price": 19500.0,
